Add brushes in ToolbarPreference>Config:Enable Customize With Ctrl + Alt held down, you simply click and drag an item to move it to its new home.Assign Brushes ShortcutsPreference>Config:Disable Customize Press and hold CTRL + ALT and click on the brush in the Brush palette. You can click on a brush icon in the Brush palette or in the Brush pop-up.Press the key on your keyboard you want to assign the interface item to or press ESC to exit.